title: Bollywood Now or Never Concert 2004 at Durban, South Africa
description:
Bollywood's "Now or Never" Concert was held in the year 2002 at ABSA Stadium, Durban, South Africa. But. the show was broadcasted on TV in the year 2004.

Bollywood super stars Amitabh Bachchan, Karisma Kapoor, Kareena Kapoor, Preity Zinta, Hrithik Roshan, Shahrukh Khan, Shilpa Shetty, Rani Mukherjee and Sushmita Sen performed in this show.
